title: I Got Stronger When I Let Go Of___// What Do You Need to Let Go Of?// Fun Month at TC (Week 4) 7 N 7
description: It is Fun Month here at TC and this Sunday is Rep Your Team Sunday! Today we had some very special guests. All 7 of these communicators are leaders at Transformation Church and today they shared what they needed to let go of in order to get STRONGER!
